      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car has been kept in a climate-controlled environment with a full service history. This is a rare find for a collector or an enthusiast seeking perfection.",
