    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that gets the job done? This vehicle is a fantastic option for anyone seeking dependable transportation at a sensible price! While it shows some expected wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a solid, functional car ready for its next owner. It\u2019s perfect for someone who values utility and honest character over a showroom finish!",
